38:09.078 --> 38:13.916
♪ Brandon wants a girl
to call his own... ♪

38:14.000 --> 38:15.543
{\an3}So of all those
women, bro,

38:15.626 --> 38:17.294
who's the nearest and
dearest to your heart?

38:17.378 --> 38:18.379
♪ Is she any kind
